              "free_text": [
                " The uncertainty associated with each cross",
                "section value represents the total experimental",
                "uncertainty calculated from the associated systematic",
                "and random uncertainties. The systematic",
                "uncertainties considered were the counter",
                "efficiencies, decay schemes, monitor cross section",
                "value, minor target isotopic impurity corrections,",
                "and summing corrections. The sources of random",
                "uncertainty were counting statistics, decay curve",
                "analyses, chemical yield determinations, timing, and",
                "target misalignment."
